# East vs West Player Generator

Generate a plausible, but comedic sounding name for an American football player.
The name can have a middle name or initial and can have a suffix, such as III.
Each player has a catchphrase based on their background, position, and physical stature.

NameGenerator {  
  State {
    Name
    CollegeOrSchoolOrPrison
    Team // East|West
    Position
    Weight
    Height
    Catchphrase
  }
  Constraints {
    The name must consist of at least a first name and a surname.
    The name must not be the name of a real player.
    The name must sound amusing, but must be able to be pronounced.
    The college, school, or prison must be real.
    The weight and height must be consistent with their position in the team, but can be exaggerated for comic purposes
    The catchphrase must not be based on any stereotypes.
  }
  /next Generate the next name and output the result in YAML
  /help Provide help
  /refine Generate another name based on the last, but with more exaggeration
  /opposite Generate another name based on the last, but with opposite characteristics
  /exaggerate Amp up the comedy by making a character's feature or trait more extreme.
  /mashup Combine elements of two or more previously generated characters.
  /nickname Generate a unique and funny nickname based on the character's existing traits.
  /backstory Provide a short, humorous backstory for the character that ties into their attributes or catchphrase.
  /random_trait Add a random and unexpected trait or hobby that contrasts with the character's football position or personality for comedic effect.
  /swap Swap one trait or attribute for its comedic opposite.
  /hometown Generate a humorous hometown for the character that plays off their name or traits.
  /rival Create a comedic rival player with contrasting traits that can be a foil to the character.
  /prop Suggest a comical prop that the player might carry around, adding a layer of absurdity.
  /quirk Introduce a small, funny quirk or habit that the character has, making them more memorable.
  /celebration Design a humorous touchdown or victory dance or action for the character.
  /motto Create a funny life motto or slogan that ties back to the character's traits or backstory.
}

